---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Portfolio - Amit Srivatsa" description="Selected work organised by theme. AI strategy, content systems, no-code automation, and strategic research." keywords="portfolio, AI strategy, content systems, automation, research, Amit Srivatsa">
  <div class="min-h-screen pt-32 pb-24 bg-[#f5f5f7]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-12 gap-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-3 tracking-tight">
            Selected work (thematic)
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-medium mb-2">
            This portfolio is organised by theme. Because patterns matter more than timelines.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-500">
            Each theme represents a way I think. And a class of problems I work on.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Themes Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

        <!-- AI strategy & adoption -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m12.83 2.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 6.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.83l8.58 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0l8.58-3.9a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.83Z"/><path d="m22 17.65-9.17 4.16a2 2 0 0 1-1.66 0L2 17.65"/><path d="m22 12.65-9.17 4.16a2 2 0 0 1-1.66 0L2 12.65"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">AI strategy & adoption</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Projects focused on: making AI usable inside real teams, designing AI-first workflows, deciding what not to automate.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-auto bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Includes</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                AI adoption roadmaps
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Internal AI agents
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Experimentation frameworks
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content systems & internal tooling -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-purple-50 text-purple-700">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 19l7-7 3 3-7 7-3-3z"/><path d="M18 13l-1.5-7.5L2 2l3.5 14.5L13 18l5-5z"/><path d="M2 2l7.586 7.586"/><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Content systems & internal tooling</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Projects focused on: turning content into systems, reducing manual marketing work, building repeatable processes.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-auto bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Includes</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Content operating models
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Internal dashboards
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Playbooks and templates
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- No-code automation & experiments -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-orange-50 text-orange-700">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">No-code automation & experiments</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Projects focused on: speed over perfection, learning by building, testing ideas cheaply.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-auto bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Includes</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                No-code tools
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Workflow automations
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Quick prototypes
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Research & strategic frameworks -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col h-full hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-green-50 text-green-700">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H20v20H6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H20"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Research & strategic frameworks</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Projects focused on: sense-making, structuring messy problems, decision support.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-auto bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Includes</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Research reports
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Strategic models
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Internal decision frameworks
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 md:p-12 text-center border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why this section exists</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          I don't believe in generic case studies. I believe in showing how I think.
          If you're considering working together. This section will help you decide faster.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">
          You're not looking for polish. You're looking for judgment.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
